  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Arth Island is a unique sandbox game, the mix of Don't starve and Terraria and some RPG elements<br>Explore a random generated world populated by dangerous creatures, build a acamp, gather resources, and craft all the items, weapons, and potion you need</h2><br>YOU ARE IN A PROCEDURALLY GENERATED WORLD AND EVERYTHING IN IT IS BREACHABLE OR COLLECTABLE<br>TAKE ADVANTAGE OF THIS TO SURVIVE THE COLD AND DANGEROUS NIGHTS<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/bf054d7c52525c8d20cf85ab8fa9c478.poster.avif?t=1667828879\" width=620 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/bf054d7c52525c8d20cf85ab8fa9c478.webm?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/bf054d7c52525c8d20cf85ab8fa9c478.mp4?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT RESOURCES</h2>Collect the basic resources to be able to make the ax and cut down the trees and the pickaxe to break the stones<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/1da81fcdb520da6d687c4dfaebb9e5d0.poster.avif?t=1667828879\" width=620 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/1da81fcdb520da6d687c4dfaebb9e5d0.webm?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/1da81fcdb520da6d687c4dfaebb9e5d0.mp4?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To extract the flesh and bones of enemies and dead animals, select the empty space in the inventory and press Space to grab and place it in the grinder<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/571e3caf674b5a6b3e2aff76e45a9ed0.poster.avif?t=1667828879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/571e3caf674b5a6b3e2aff76e45a9ed0.webm?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/571e3caf674b5a6b3e2aff76e45a9ed0.mp4?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVOLUTION</h2>hand-to-hand combat?, a shower of arrows on enemies? Or would you rather burn them with magic?<br>you choose which skill to perfect<br><br>3 starting weapons<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/82315a12cf1041d7d0e60693243bd87c.poster.avif?t=1667828879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/82315a12cf1041d7d0e60693243bd87c.webm?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/82315a12cf1041d7d0e60693243bd87c.mp4?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Attack cadence affects all 3 classes and can be found in the talent tree<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/2756644c136accc373f09a50ef262508.poster.avif?t=1667828879\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1987280/extras/2756644c136accc373f09a50ef262508.webm?t=1667828879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"